Sanno,<br><br>
The essence of the eagle is contained in its lonely vigil and need for solitude.  It is one of the few that is totally loyal and seeks nothing but its own peace.<br><br>
You have captured a piece of that noble spirit in your poem.  I to seek solitude and you put that feeling to words in way that I will not forget.<br><br>
When this sight moves follow it and bring your poetry.  We will all gain from the visions you paint with words.<br>

